    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n9631" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέρης</span></b>  (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χείρ</span>, i. e. under one's hand), dat. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέρηι</span>, acc. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέρηα</span>, pl.
            <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέρηες</span>, neut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χέρεια</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">low, humble, weak, mean, poor</span>, the
          positive to <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">χείρων, χερείων, χειρότερος,
            χερειότερος</span>. With gen. it has the force of a comp., <i><span class="en">Il. 4.400</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            14.176</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
